93
00:05:33,700 --> 00:05:36,460
 And this is the guy we should worship.

94
00:05:36,460 --> 00:05:39,380
 And this is the guy who has the most power.

95
00:05:39,380 --> 00:05:43,300
 (speaking in foreign language)

96
00:05:53,020 --> 00:05:56,900
 And then, you know, the Babylonian myth

