00:06:32,500 --> 00:06:33,780
 and create a dry ground.

108
00:06:33,780 --> 00:06:35,940
 And then he rules over the gods

109
00:06:35,940 --> 00:06:39,260
 and put order in the cosmos

110
00:06:39,260 --> 00:06:42,740
 and create a city, the greatest city of Babylon.

111
00:06:42,740 --> 00:06:47,740
 And he became the final authority of the entire cosmos.

112
00:06:47,740 --> 00:06:51,980
 (speaking in foreign language)

113
00:06:52,180 --> 00:06:56,100
 (speaking in foreign language)

