 may be Chicago, or may be your home city.

146
00:08:52,420 --> 00:08:56,260
 Some sort of city that feels like home.

147
00:08:56,260 --> 00:09:01,340
 (speaking in foreign language)

148
00:09:17,140 --> 00:09:20,420
 And for the people of God in the Old Testament especially,

149
00:09:20,420 --> 00:09:23,180
 the key city is which one?

150
