00:09:31,220 --> 00:09:32,340
 They are the same.

154
00:09:32,340 --> 00:09:34,740
 And that is why some of the psalms

155
00:09:34,740 --> 00:09:37,340
 are called Songs of Zion.

156
00:09:37,340 --> 00:09:40,260
 Songs of Zion, praising the city of Zion.

157
00:09:40,260 --> 00:09:44,860
 And Psalm 46 is actually one of the Zion songs.

158
00:09:44,860 --> 00:09:49,300
 And because this city is worthy of our praise

159
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:53,060
 and our attention because God dwells in the midst of Zion.

160
00:09:53,060 --> 00:09:58,060
 And God's people do not need to fear.

161
00:09:58,060 --> 00:10:02,100
 (speaking in foreign language)

162
00:10:13,100 --> 00:10:15,300
 Well, let's read the four to seven here.

