00:14:01,620 --> 00:14:05,420
 on almost every wall inside her house.

214
00:14:05,420 --> 00:14:10,420
 And this is one of the ways she coped

215
00:14:10,420 --> 00:14:15,100
 with the terror brought by ISIS.

216
00:14:15,100 --> 00:14:20,260
 (speaking in foreign language)

217
00:14:32,380 --> 00:14:35,540
 And when she was terrified, she was trying to calm

218
00:14:35,540 --> 00:14:37,140
 the fear in her heart.

219
00:14:37,140 --> 00:14:40,700
 And that's why she put the name of Jesus in Arabic,

