00:15:53,460 --> 00:15:55,180
 The Lord Almighty is with us.

242
00:15:55,180 --> 00:15:57,740
 The God of Jacob is our fortress.

243
00:15:57,740 --> 00:16:01,660
 (speaking in foreign language)

